      • startActiveServices

        public void startActiveServices()
                         throws IOException
        Start services for BackupNode.

        The following services should be muted (not run or not pass any control commands to DataNodes) on BackupNode: LeaseManager.Monitor protected by SafeMode. BlockManager.ReplicationMonitor protected by SafeMode. HeartbeatManager.Monitor protected by SafeMode. DecommissionManager.Monitor need to prohibit refreshNodes(). PendingReplicationBlocks.PendingReplicationMonitor harmless, because ReplicationMonitor is muted.
